# Keep only the 5 essential files on GitHub
# Exclude all noise: logs, templates, histories, casting, sessions

# Templates — boilerplate, no value on GitHub
templates/

# Session & orchestration logs — local diagnostics
log/
orchestration-log/
sessions/

# Casting machinery — internal Squad plumbing
casting/
casting-history.json
casting-policy.json
casting-registry.json

# Agent history files — personal/local knowledge
agents/*/history.md
agents/*/history-archive.md
agents/_alumni/

# Loose root-level template/reference files
charter.md
scribe-charter.md
roster.md
history.md
orchestration-log.md
run-output.md
raw-agent-output.md
multi-agent-format.md
constraint-tracking.md
issue-lifecycle.md
plugin-marketplace.md
mcp-config.md
skill.md
copilot-instructions.md
config.json
gitmsg.tmp

# Identity/wisdom — local context
identity/

# Skills — earned knowledge, kept locally
skills/

# Decisions inbox — transient, merged by Scribe
decisions/
